item.title: Mac下permission_denied
item.description: 解决 open /usr/local/go/pkg/darwin_amd64/runtime/cgo.a: permission denied 1 2 3 4 $ sudo chown -R [用户名] /usr/local/go/pkg/darwin_amd64/ $ whoami uyaki $ sudo chown -R uyaki /usr/local/go/pkg/darwin_amd64/
